---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Dispensary Security Requirements | Maine Dispensary Guide" description="Complete guide to security requirements for Maine cannabis dispensaries. Includes surveillance, alarm systems, access control, and compliance requirements.">
  <article>
    <header>
      <h1>Security Requirements</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Understanding Maine's dispensary security requirements and best practices</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Maine requires comprehensive security systems for all cannabis dispensaries. These requirements are designed to protect inventory, employees, and customers while ensuring compliance with state regulations.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Video Surveillance</h2>
      <p>Maine mandates 24/7 video surveillance of all areas of the facility.</p>
      <h3>Requirements:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Recording at minimum 720p resolution (1080p recommended)</li>
        <li>Continuous recording 24/7</li>
        <li>Retention of video for minimum 90 days</li>
        <li>Coverage of all entry/exit points</li>
        <li>Coverage of all areas where cannabis is stored</li>
        <li>Coverage of point-of-sale areas</li>
        <li>Coverage of parking lots and exterior</li>
        <li>Remote viewing capability for law enforcement</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Alarm Systems</h2>
      <p>Professional monitored alarm systems are required.</p>
      <h3>Required Features:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Burglar alarm on all exterior doors and windows</li>
        <li>Motion detectors in interior spaces</li>
        <li>Glass break sensors on ground-floor windows</li>
        <li>24/7 professional monitoring</li>
        <li>Direct connection to monitoring service</li>
        <li>Cellular backup (in case phone line is cut)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Access Control</h2>
      <p>Limit access to sensitive areas within the facility.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Electronic keycard or biometric access for restricted areas</li>
        <li>Visitor log and escort requirements</li>
        <li>Employee-only zones clearly marked</li>
        <li>Secure entry/exit procedures</li>
        <li>Master key control and logging</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Secure Storage</h2>
      <p>Cannabis inventory must be stored securely.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Steel-reinforced vault or safe for high-value products</li>
        <li>Locked storage for all cannabis products</li>
        <li>Separate secure area for large inventory</li>
        <li>Proper ventilation for product storage</li>
        <li>Climate control to maintain product integrity</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Employee Security</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Background checks required for all employees</li>
        <li>Training on security protocols</li>
        <li>Cash handling procedures</li>
        <li>Robbery prevention training</li>
        <li>Emergency response procedures</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Estimated Costs</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>System</th><th>Initial Cost</th><th>Monthly Cost</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Video Surveillance</td><td>$15,000 - $35,000</td><td>$200 - $500</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Alarm System</td><td>$5,000 - $15,000</td><td>$100 - $300</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Access Control</td><td>$3,000 - $10,000</td><td>$50 - $150</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Safe/Vault</td><td>$5,000 - $15,000</td><td>$0</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Total</strong></td><td><strong>$28,000 - $75,000</strong></td><td><strong>$350 - $950</strong></td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Compliance Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Document all security procedures thoroughly</li>
        <li>Conduct regular security audits</li>
        <li>Maintain logs of all security incidents</li>
        <li>Test systems regularly</li>
        <li>Keep software/firmware updated</li>
        <li>Coordinate with local law enforcement</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>24/7 video surveillance is mandatory</li>
        <li>90-day video retention required</li>
        <li>Professional alarm monitoring required</li>
        <li>Access control for restricted areas</li>
        <li>Employee background checks mandatory</li>
        <li>Budget $30K-75K for security systems</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>Requirements subject to change. Verify current Maine Office of Cannabis Policy requirements.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  section h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  section h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
</style>
